com.membase.jtap.message
Class HeaderMessage

java.lang.Object
  com.membase.jtap.message.HeaderMessage
Direct Known Subclasses:
RequestMessage, ResponseMessage
public class HeaderMessage
extends java.lang.Object

The HeaderMessage implements the header of a tap message. This class cannot be instantiated. To create tap stream messages see the RequestMessage and ResponseMessage classes.
